      "content": "wait i already stopped taking it for a bit and it felt better but now i'm feeling really anxious about missing doses. if i just drink a ton more water and maybe take some extra magnesium, will that help stabilize things so i don't have to go to the doctor right away? i'm trying to avoid the clinic if i can.",
